   GOLD-MARKETPLACE (Undated) _ Jean-Marie Eveillard, the portfolio
manager of Sogen Gold fund, recalls a recent comment by Alan
Greenspan, the Federal Reserve chairman, that gold is still the
``ultimate form of payment.'' ``You can't say that about copper and
pork bellies,'' Eveillard said. No, you can't. But you can't bank
on gold anymore, either. By Jonathan Fuerbringer.
