   QWEST-USWEST (Undated) _ Two years ago, just before Qwest
Communications International Inc. first offered stock to the
public, Joseph Nacchio, who had just become Qwest's chief
executive, said he wanted to create a ``full-service communications
provider.'' On Sunday, by launching a pair of hostile bids, Nacchio
proved his strategy was real. By Seth Schiesel.
