<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-15 14:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5978 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GRIEF-STUDIES-HNS &LR;      06-15 0710
