<DOCNO> NYT19990615.0107 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-15 14:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5981 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-POSTPARTUM-BLUES-HNS &LR;      06-15 0711
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-POSTPARTUM-BLUES-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
STRESS MAY INTERFERE WITH THE THRILL OF GIVING BIRTH 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Bellevue Woman's Hospital is CQ)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By SYLVIA WOOD  
 c.1999 Albany Times Union  
