Spurs; they're in virgin territory. They also are the first team
from the defunct American Basketball Association to appear in the
NBA Finals. By Peter May.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-COLUMN (Undated) _ US women have taken the initiative in
expanding the scope of soccer in recent years. But the pioneers, as
in men's soccer, were the English. By Frank Dell'Apa.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-REVOLUTION (Undated) _ Walter Zenga has spent the last few
months trying to hermetically seal the Revolution defense. But
leaks have been springing up all over the field lately. By Frank
Dell'Apa.
</P>
<P>
   RAC-COLUMN (Undated) _ Simply put, Silver Charm went sour. It
happens to many thoroughbreds: They reach the point where they
don't want to race anymore. By Ron Indrisano.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
