SAN FRANCISCO _  &UR; CLASSIC-Bi-Rite Market &LR;  _ Sam Mogannam, a former
restaurant chef, has renovated Bi-Rite Market to its classic look.
Customers are welcomed by many of Sam's restaurant staff _ former
restaurant managers work the registers and chefs cook the prepared
foods.
<P>
   Signs of dedication to service and quality foods are visible
throughout the store: farm carts overflow with fresh produce,
artisan breads and cheeses, and the deli counter is stocked with
items like house-smoked lox and roasted chicken. &QL; 
