</P>
<P>
   In that case Circuit City, CompUSA, Office Max and Staples,
among others, are being sued for not warning consumers about
potential Y2K problems in computers and software they sold.
</P>
<P>
   ``The clear intent of this litigation is a large settlement,''
McCain said. ``It's not to remedy any injury or failure.''
</P>
<P>
   The Senate legislation will be reconciled with a similar House
bill that was passed last month.
</P>
<P>
   Feinstein said she will work with the administration to make the
measure more acceptable to the White House.
</P>
<P>
   (Jennifer Corbett Dooren can be reached at 202-298-6920 and at
jennifer(at)hearstdc.com)
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
