<P>
   22. Jean Harlow
</P>
<P>
   23. Carole Lombard
</P>
<P>
   24. Mary Pickford
</P>
<P>
   25. Ava Gardner
</P>
<P>
   Bob Longino writes for the Atlanta Journal-Constitution.
</P>
