of June 16 and thereafter. The stories will carry the ``f''
financial news category code unless otherwise noted. For questions
about stories, contact Stewart Slavin at the Daily News, (818)
713-3701.
</P>
<P>
   SUPERIOR-DEALS (Los Angeles) _ Superior Industries Inc.
announced deals worth $250 million annually on Tuesday, and the
maker of automotive parts said it needs to build a new plant to
handle the extra business. By Enrique Rivero.
</P>
