<P>
   KOSOVO-RDP (Pristina, Yugoslavia) _ Serb forces are expected to
meet the deadline to be out of southern Kosovo by Tuesday evening.
A Russian convoy is en route to the resupply their forces at the
airport here. By Steven Lee Myers.
