<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-15 20:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6522 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-ARATON-COLUMN-NYT     06-15 1055
