<DOCNO> NYT19990615.0312 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-15 21:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6607 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SILICON-REPUBS-NYT &LR;      06-15 1186
