for a friend to take a look at bloodstained jackets and other
clothing he found on Tuesday in a field suspected of being a mass
grave. Witnesses claim over 30 ethnic Albanians were executed near
here in March and buried in this field by Serb forces. (Tyler
Hicks/New York Times Photo)
